metadata.name: MetaToys #1
metadata.description: MetaToys is a blockchain technology based trendy Metaverse, centered on Gamefi and Socialfi, which provides users with a brand-new life experience in the games created both by official team and community users through UGC tools.Players can transfer NFTs assets to different game worlds or resell them to others.Each Meta Toy Original from different time and space was called Time-Space Childï¼ŒThe first 10,000 arrivals of Toys' Land were called Meta Toys Original. The Meta God has given them the extraordinary ability to travel through time, space and other worlds,while ordinary Meta Toys only can travel back and forth in Toys' Land and its corresponding sub-worlds.
